{"tid":1243453,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[泰拳打火龍] 根據經典遊戲改編的《Monster Hunter》(魔物獵人)在上海國際電影節曝光了首款預告","createTime":"2019-06-19T12:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T06:11:13.000Z","uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b778bf371391dd6b613703c950d63f17ba089c8b","tid":1243453,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T12:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DSJOwVq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDSJOwVq.jpg&h=53281226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《魔物獵人》（英語：Monster Hunter）是一部未上映的美國奇幻動作驚悚片，由保羅&middot;W&middot;S&middot;安德森執導和撰寫劇本。電影改編自同名遊戲，由卡普空、Impact Pictures和康斯坦丁影業製片，主演包括米娜&middot;祖華域芝、柏朗&middot;伊雲(Tony Jaa)、T.I.、朗&middot;柏曼、迪亞哥&middot;伯尼塔和山崎紘菜。<br />\n<br />\n劇情<br />\n故事敘述一支聯合國的部隊進入了通往另一個世界的穿越口，並在那協同其住民與巨型怪物戰鬥。該世界的人類必須與聯合國部隊們共同努力守護其穿越口，以防止怪物透過入口來侵襲地球。<br />\n<br />\n首款預告:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Nmia.Gaming/videos/384376438851798/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNmia.Gaming%2Fvideos%2F384376438851798%2F&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=e898e1cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Nmia.Gaming/videos/384376438851798/</a>"},{"pid":"ef54dc1f3b77e0bf70b5ee51df8972a195efdf37","tid":1243453,"uid":75050,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T13:01:53.000Z","msg":"據此前日本消息，飾演AIBO的是山崎紘菜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cinematoday.jp/news/N0105562\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinematoday.jp%2Fnews%2FN0105562&d=26VZ%2FvgZZ8DFpCmOvUDyu7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=dd822651\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cinematoday.jp/news/N0105562</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.cinematoday.jp/a/N0105562/_size_640x/_v_1544614321/main.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.cinematoday.jp%2Fa%2FN0105562%2F_size_640x%2F_v_1544614321%2Fmain.jpg%3F&h=627db7a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pi